text: 4-Months of Google Play Music & YouTube Red Subscription [ google.com ] Free (New Subscribers) This is valid for New Subscribers only . You must sign into your Google account to purchase. Upon completion of your 4-Month trial, the monthly rate to continue service is $9.99. You may cancel at any time before your trial end date and still receive the full 4-months of membership benefits without incurring further charges.
